7
00:00:46,613 --> 00:00:48,415
- You see anything?
- Just the body.

8
00:00:48,415 --> 00:00:50,283
Thomas Marchek, pedophile.

9
00:00:50,283 --> 00:00:52,952
- You say Marchek?
- Yeah.

10
00:00:52,952 --> 00:00:54,354
You know the guy?

11
00:00:54,354 --> 00:00:56,056
He raped a
seven-year-old girl.

12
00:00:56,056 --> 00:00:58,091
Left her cut up and
unconscious in a drainpipe.

13
00:00:58,091 --> 00:00:59,492
Yeah, I know.

14
00:00:59,492 --> 00:01:01,928
And how are you so tuned in?

15
00:01:01,928 --> 00:01:03,730
I'm just doing my job.

16
00:01:03,730 --> 00:01:05,519
All right. Sir, did you
touch the body?

17
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:08,101
- I know better.
- Not even to check for vitals?

18
00:01:08,101 --> 00:01:09,954
Shorteye's head was
practically blown off.

19
00:01:09,954 --> 00:01:11,687
Look, if you want to talk to me,

20
00:01:11,687 --> 00:01:14,074
here's a card with my numbers...

21
00:01:14,074 --> 00:01:15,802
home and work.

22
00:01:16,409 --> 00:01:18,206
It's nice to meet you.

23
00:01:20,513 --> 00:01:23,683
Five years ago,
I put this guy away.

24
00:01:23,683 --> 00:01:24,784
You SVU?

25
00:01:24,784 --> 00:01:26,853
Yeah, Benson, Stabler.
Who called us?

26
00:01:26,853 --> 00:01:29,355
You got three shots,
point blank to the face.

27
00:01:29,355 --> 00:01:30,857
Nine mil.

28
00:01:30,857 --> 00:01:33,927
Wouldn't be surprised if the slugs
turn out to be hollow point.

29
00:01:33,927 --> 00:01:36,763
- Made quite a statement.
- And a mess.

30
00:01:36,763 --> 00:01:39,365
Now, why'd you call us in?
This is a homicide.

31
00:01:39,365 --> 00:01:41,668
Chief of Detective
reassigned by request.

32
00:01:41,668 --> 00:01:44,037
You sent the guy up.
I guess that's why you're catching.

33
00:01:44,037 --> 00:01:45,705
This is a dead ex-con.

34
00:01:45,705 --> 00:01:48,007
This is not a victim
of a sex crime. Was he raped?

35
00:01:48,007 --> 00:01:50,043
Do his wounds suggest
anything sexual in nature?

36
00:01:50,043 --> 00:01:53,313
I feel for you, pal,
but this comes from above.

37
00:01:53,313 --> 00:01:54,714
Your problem's not with me.

38
00:01:54,714 --> 00:01:56,316
Who made the request?

39
00:01:56,316 --> 00:01:58,909
A Captain Cragen.

40
00:02:02,188 --> 00:02:05,452
Elliot, give him a chance
to explain.

41
00:02:10,463 --> 00:02:12,055
Why?

42
00:02:12,665 --> 00:02:13,766
Excuse me?

43
00:02:13,766 --> 00:02:15,535
Thomas Marchek kidnapped
Corrine Branson...

44
00:02:15,535 --> 00:02:17,904
tortured her at knifepoint,
and left her for dead.

45
00:02:17,904 --> 00:02:19,005
I read the file.

46
00:02:19,005 --> 00:02:20,707
I was ready to cap
that dirtbag myself.

47
00:02:20,707 --> 00:02:22,442
Now you expect me to
work his homicide?

48
00:02:22,442 --> 00:02:24,477
One Police Plaza does.

49
00:02:24,477 --> 00:02:27,002
They asked me to take it,
I said "yes".

50
00:02:29,415 --> 00:02:31,718
To polish your political apple?

51
00:02:31,718 --> 00:02:34,420
It's delicate territory
and you're familiar with the players.

52
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:36,389
- I'll fill Homicide in.
- You go talk to the parents.

53
00:02:36,389 --> 00:02:39,092
I'll talk to the parents and tell them
the good news about Marchek.

54
00:02:39,092 --> 00:02:40,927
But I am not telling them
that they're suspects.

55
00:02:40,927 --> 00:02:43,363
According to the Chief,
the girl's mother threatened Marchek...

56
00:02:43,363 --> 00:02:44,497
