267
00:12:58,344 --> 00:13:02,905
What I would do to him.
How I would make him suffer!

268
00:13:05,684 --> 00:13:08,084
Tell me what happened last night.

269
00:13:10,689 --> 00:13:12,825
I followed him...

270
00:13:12,825 --> 00:13:14,894
from, um...

271
00:13:14,894 --> 00:13:19,296
from the meat market to some bar
