277
00:13:38,250 --> 00:13:40,445
But I couldn't do it.

278
00:13:41,554 --> 00:13:46,125
Every night I had the chance
and I just, I couldn't do it.

279
00:13:46,125 --> 00:13:49,028
And then somebody else did it for me.

280
00:13:49,028 --> 00:13:50,830
Yeah.

281
00:13:59,438 --> 00:14:03,032
- I don't have a confession.
