289
00:14:27,233 --> 00:14:30,202
Same MO, 9mm, hollow-point slugs.

290
00:14:30,202 --> 00:14:32,571
Guess that lets Lindsay off the hook.

291
00:14:32,571 --> 00:14:35,437
Puts us on the trail of 
