313
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:51,574
was raped in prison and got HIV.

314
00:15:53,419 --> 00:15:55,614
He suffered, too.

315
00:15:58,590 --> 00:16:00,559
My brother-in-law said to expect you.

316
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:01,710
Your brother-in-law?

317
00:16:01,710 --> 00:16:03,696
Yeah, he's a patrol cop in Queens.

318
00:16:03,696 --> 00:16:05,664
Figured my little run-in
with Craig the pervert...

319
00:16:05,664 --> 00:16:07,166
would put me at the top of your list.

320
00:16:07,166 --> 00:16:09,668
