321
00:16:09,668 --> 00:16:11,704
I kicked him out of my store.

322
00:16:11,704 --> 00:16:13,405
And kept kicking?

323
00:16:13,405 --> 00:16:14,974
He's a rapist.

324
00:16:14,974 --> 00:16:16,463
