326
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:24,149
What am I supposed to do,
wait for him to rape them, too?

327
00:16:24,149 --> 00:16:26,585
Where were you last night
between 8:00 and 10:00?

328
00:16:26,585 --> 00:16:27,720
Right here.

329
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:29,221
I'm open till 11:00 every night.

330
00:16:29,221 --> 00:16:31,523
And I got plenty of customers
who'll vouch for that.

331
00:16:31,523 --> 00:16:34,393
Who enlightened you about
Mr. Moss' background?

332
00:16:34,393 --> 00:16:36,462
A Citizen Watch guy came in here 
with a flyer...

333
00:16:36,462 --> 00:16:38,330
Asking me to post them on my window.

334
00:16:38,330 --> 00:16:39,965
I asked for extras.

335
00:16:39,965 --> 00:16:42,868
He said this guy Moss
raped a mother of four.

336
00:16:42,868 --> 00:16:45,371
Predators like him, they never stop.

337
00:16:45,371 --> 00:16:48,974
I run a family business.
This kind of scum ain't welcome here.

338
00:16:48,974 --> 00:16:51,977
You have any idea where we might
be able to find this Citizen Watch guy?

339
00:16:51,977 --> 00:16:55,347
Yeah, sure, they rent a space in
the Rec Center, couple of blocks down.

340
00:16:55,347 --> 00:16:59,681
They do a good job, too.
I haven't had a break-in in two years.

341
00:17:05,591 --> 00:17:08,160
Hello, Detectives, good to see you again.

342
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:10,525
This is not a social visit.

343
00:17:11,630 --> 00:17:13,899
We'd like you to stop
