344
00:17:13,899 --> 00:17:15,534
We're not breaking any laws.

345
00:17:15,534 --> 00:17:17,202
That remains to be seen.

346
00:17:17,202 --> 00:17:19,538
Mr. Pulham assaulted a man 
on your flyer.

347
00:17:19,538 --> 00:17:21,940
And now two of them are dead.

348
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:23,609
I'm sorry to hear that.

349
00:17:23,609 --> 00:17:26,178
We only try to inform and prevent.

350
00:17:26,178 --> 00:17:29,348
You're inciting people to break the law.
To commit murder.

351
00:17:29,348 --> 00:17:31,383
- That's a long reach, isn't it?
- Is it?

352
00:17:31,383 --> 00:17:33,218
We've got two dead men...

353
00:17:33,218 --> 00:17:34,887
Flyers that you've distributed...

354
00:17:34,887 --> 00:17:38,457
and Citizen Watch members
at both crime scenes.

355
00:17:38,457 --> 00:17:39,792
Are we suspects?

356
00:17:39,792 --> 00:17:43,762
We'd like a list of your members,
names, addresses, phone numbers, please.

357
00:17:43,762 --> 00:17:45,631
You know, we're only 
protecting ourselves

358
00:17:45,631 --> 00:17:48,567
against these rapists 
because you won't.

359
00:17:48,567 --> 00:17:51,670
The system puts them in our
neighborhoods and then turns its back.

360
00:17:51,670 --> 00:17:53,806
And where exactly would you 
