364
00:18:10,522 --> 00:18:12,991
Much as I hate it,
there's nothing we can do.

365
00:18:12,991 --> 00:18:15,060
Protecting rapists now.

366
00:18:15,060 --> 00:18:16,895
To shield us from lawsuits...

367
00:18:16,895 --> 00:18:20,558
and to keep anyone else on
that flyer from being murdered.

368
00:18:21,133 --> 00:18:23,735
Now the remaining two parolees 
on the list...

369
00:18:23,735 --> 00:18:27,039
Trent Wills and James Campbell,
are to get round-the-clock protection.

370
00:18:27,039 --> 00:18:28,640
