371
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:32,576
about the honest, hard-working
people who actually need us?

372
00:18:34,379 --> 00:18:38,784
These men have rights and we have
jobs to do. Anything else?

373
00:18:38,784 --> 00:18:41,153
Ballistics came back
