388
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:19,691
Yes, sir.

389
00:19:19,691 --> 00:19:21,994
I get enough crap from the politicians.

390
00:19:21,994 --> 00:19:25,364
I don't need any from my own detectives.

391
00:19:25,364 --> 00:19:27,666
