395
00:19:39,378 --> 00:19:41,013
No.

396
00:19:41,013 --> 00:19:44,149
Anybody been stalking you?
Giving you attitude?

397
00:19:44,149 --> 00:19:46,151
Yeah.

398
00:19:46,151 --> 00:19:48,720
Two fat, ugly, old broads
with matching windbreakers.

399
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:52,624
I doubled back and spooked
the hell out of them.

400
00:19:52,624 --> 00:19:55,394
A fun time was had by all.

401
00:19:55,394 --> 00:19:57,329
