00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:17,948
Watch me, Daddy!

407
00:20:19,818 --> 00:20:22,521
Your mother-in-law said 
we'd find you here.

408
00:20:22,521 --> 00:20:24,957
We try to live as normally as possible...

409
00:20:24,957 --> 00:20:27,759
but that watch group is making
our lives miserable.

410
00:20:27,759 --> 00:20:31,563
After they put me on that flyer,
my boss fired me.

411
00:20:31,563 --> 00:20:33,565
Didn't want a pervert selling insurance.

412
00:20:33,565 --> 00:20:35,130
Can you blame them for being afraid?

