447
00:21:59,251 --> 00:22:02,220
You're here about Gloria?

448
00:22:02,220 --> 00:22:04,187
Come this way.

449
00:22:05,724 --> 00:22:08,794
We understand you were with
Gloria and Thomas Marchek...

450
00:22:08,794 --> 00:22:11,563
when a man from Citizen
Watch approached you.

451
00:22:11,563 --> 00:22:13,265
