455
00:22:20,138 --> 00:22:21,707
Yes, he's this one.

456
00:22:21,707 --> 00:22:23,909
Do you think he had something
to do with Thomas' murder?

457
00:22:23,909 --> 00:22:26,678
Do you remember what he said 
in the restaurant?

458
00:22:26,678 --> 00:22:28,347
Nothing to me.

459
00:22:28,347 --> 00:22:32,351
He showed Thomas his gun
and told him to watch out.

460
00:22:32,351 --> 00:22:34,686
