466
00:22:45,997 --> 00:22:48,967
- Did he say anything?
- Awful stuff about Tommy.

467
00:22:48,967 --> 00:22:52,270
He said if I knew what was good for me,
I'd leave him and never see him again.

468
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:54,773
One time Tommy came in
and he was talking to Glo...

469
00:22:54,773 --> 00:22:56,842
I thought for sure there was
gonna be hell to pay.

470
00:22:56,842 --> 00:22:57,681
What happened?

471
00:22:57,681 --> 00:22:59,244
Tommy grabbed Winfield by the shirt

472
00:22:59,244 --> 00:23:00,679
