479
00:23:15,827 --> 00:23:19,431
At the rate this guy's going, we're gonna
have to assign another protection detail.

480
00:23:19,431 --> 00:23:22,035
Dispatch just got a call from
the Campbell residence.

481
00:23:22,035 --> 00:23:26,104
