495
00:23:57,402 --> 00:23:59,070
Coming up the street he grabbed me,

496
00:23:59,070 --> 00:24:00,872
and told me to get out of the neighborhood.

497
00:24:00,872 --> 00:24:02,841
When I told him to go to hell...

498
00:24:02,841 --> 00:24:06,445
he said if I didn't listen, I was gonna
end up like the other two guys.

499
00:24:06,445 --> 00:24:08,854
